        ********
        Features
        ********
        
        Version 0.1
        """""""""""
        
        * Resource API
        * Plan API
        * Bank API
        * Ledger API
        * Cross-resource dependencies
        
        Limitations
        ***********
        
        * Only 1 Bank plugin per Protection Plan
        * Automatic object discovery not supported
        
        
